---
title: HiTicket - Overall System Flow
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    actor Agent
    participant FE as React App
    participant API as Express API
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant Email as Gmail API

    User->>FE: Register / Login (2FA)
    FE->>API: POST /auth/register or /auth/login
    API->>DB: Verify credentials, issue JWT
    DB-->>API: User data
    API-->>FE: JWT token

    User->>FE: Create ticket via Chatbot wizard
    FE->>API: POST /api/tickets + JWT
    API->>DB: Auto-assign agent, save ticket TKT-NNNN
    DB-->>API: Saved ticket
    API-->>FE: 201 ticket created
    API--)Email: Confirmation email async

    Agent->>FE: View and update ticket
    FE->>API: PATCH /api/tickets/:id + JWT
    API->>DB: Update status, log history
    DB-->>API: Updated ticket
    API-->>FE: 200 updated ticket
    API--)Email: Notify user of update async

    note over API, DB: Cron Jobs run automatically
    API->>DB: Hourly SLA check, daily auto-close, due-date reminders, weekly digest
    API--)Email: Automated alerts async
